trans-unit.source: Converts the <xref:System.Windows.Window.DialogResult*> property, which is a <xref:System.Nullable%601> value of type <xref:System.Boolean>, to and from other types.
## XAML Text Usage
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> class.

<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> does not support converting from other types to <xref:System.Windows.Window.DialogResult*> (a <xref:System.Nullable%601> value of type <xref:System.Boolean>).
A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides a format context.
A <xref:System.Type> that represents the type to convert from.
A <xref:System.Boolean> that always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> does not support converting from <xref:System.Windows.Window.DialogResult*> (a <xref:System.Nullable%601> value of type <xref:System.Boolean>) to other types.
A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides a format context.
A <xref:System.Type> that represents the type to convert to.
A <xref:System.Boolean> that always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> does not support converting from <xref:System.Windows.Window.DialogResult*> (a <xref:System.Nullable%601> value of type <xref:System.Boolean>) to other types.
A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides a format context.
The <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> to use as the current culture.
If <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> is passed, the current culture is assumed.
The <xref:System.Object> to convert.
Always raises <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
ConvertFrom is called.
